<td align="center"><b>
<i>Epeolus compactus</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cresson, 1878</font></b><br>
<small><i>Epeolus crucis </i>Cockerell, 1904; <i>Epeolus hitei </i>Cockerell, 1908; <i>Triepeolus gabrielis </i>Cockerell, 1910; <i>Epeolus geminatus </i>Cockerell and Sandhouse, 1924</small><p>
